description:
Tina McElroy Ansa is a little girl when her father&rsquo;s business goes under and her family must leave their beloved, expansive home.  Alan Rabinowitz treks through the Himalayas to study the Taron, a dying race of people, and makes discoveries about himself. &nbsp;
Elna Baker must tell her Mormon parents that she has made an irreversible change in her life.
&nbsp;
